I’m excited to announce my partnership with Russellville Fitness & Nutrition!! 🏋🏻‍♀️🥗👟

RFN is a faith-centered, family gym offering high-intensity training for all fitness levels. Memberships include personalized nutritional guidance so you can reach your goals in the gym and in the kitchen. RFN also offers a variety of class formats with morning and evening times to fit busy schedules.

ATU students!!💚💛 When you sign up under my name, you’ll receive $10 off your monthly plan plus your first week of classes free!

Questions or ready to join? Message me and I’ll get you set up.

Thunder Up!

I was lucky enough to tour Paycom Arena and the Oklahoma City Thunder Corporate Office. It was fascinating to go behind the scenes and glance into the business side of an NBA championship team, specifically the social media team. The social media crew was very insightful and welcoming.

Inside the Champions Arena!

Yesterday I was given the pleasure of being shown around Paycom Arena (Oklahoma City Thunder’s home Arena)! I could not be more thankful for the experience an it is truly crazy to see everything from a behind the scenes corporate perspective!
#okcthunder #atubusiness #goodasgold #accounting #marketing

Career Connection #1. I enjoyed hearing about Russellville insurance agency yesterday at the ATU business career connection. Insurance can be a tricky field so it was cool to learn the benefits of having a local agency in your corner, and the employment opportunities they offer.

Great day at the career connection with Russellville Insurance Agency! A family orientated insurance agency with friendly employees. 💡
Was really interesting to hear about the intern/full job opportunity that they have to offer! Also interesting to also learn about all the different types of insurance, not just personal insurance (cars and homes) but also cool commercial insurance such as small to medium sized businesses and restaurants!! 💫
